{"type":"message","id":"7e465785","parentId":"9474987f","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:20:11.057Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我为赵丛算今日运势。这是一个八字命理分析的任务。我需要：\n\n1. 首先确认今天的日期 - 2026年3月6日\n2. 根据她提供的出生信息（1998年1月11日，阳历）计算八字\n3. 查找今日的吉凶信息\n4. 给出运势分析\n\n让我先查看一下是否有相关的工具或文件可以帮助我完成这个任务。根据AGENTS.md和SOUL.md，团队中有\"袁天罡\"是风水命理师。\n\n我应该使用 tavily-search 或其他方式搜索今日运势信息，或者使用之前保存的运势分析工具。\n\n让我先看看有没有现成的运势分析脚本或工具。","thinkingSignature":"12fcc95ef2d3fb997bc5303ad0cc5772cee9e5418f6be6796705162e80ab8e80"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_80nag2ua1t6o_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace/deliverables/fortunes/"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":20,"output":182,"cacheRead":4429,"cacheWrite":10956,"totalTokens":15587,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772778000056}}
{"type":"message","id":"54e6f3f5","parentId":"7e465785","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:20:11.093Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_80nag2ua1t6o_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"total 8\ndrwxr-xr-x@  3 lynch  staff    96 Mar  5 20:17 .\ndrwxr-xr-x@ 11 lynch  staff   352 Mar  5 22:23 ..\n-rw-r--r--@  1 lynch  staff  1870 Mar  5 18:41 daily_fortune.py"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"total 8\ndrwxr-xr-x@  3 lynch  staff    96 Mar  5 20:17 .\ndrwxr-xr-x@ 11 lynch  staff   352 Mar  5 22:23 ..\n-rw-r--r--@  1 lynch  staff  1870 Mar  5 18:41 daily_fortune.py","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772778011091}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7b26d21","parentId":"54e6f3f5","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:20:13.645Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"有一个 daily_fortune.py 文件，让我查看它的内容看看是否能用来分析运势。","thinkingSignature":"b7c3db5dbab2dd7848e2815833f85eed7c3205eb2e4b20a36189e343692cf95c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_15o8tgnfcovh_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/deliverables/fortunes/daily_fortune.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":414,"output":59,"cacheRead":15273,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15746,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772778011093}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d028d47","parentId":"e7b26d21","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:20:13.669Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_15o8tgnfcovh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n每日运势任务\n- 德国时间 8 点执行\n- 调用袁天罡算命\n- 发邮件给赵丛和 Lynch\n\"\"\"\n\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 邮箱配置\nGMAIL = 'yuanlynch@gmail.com'\nAPP_PASSWORD = 'jsnjyjwpavymplev'\nTO_ZHAOCONG = 'zhaocongzhaocong0111@gmail.com'\nTO_LYNCH = 'l1cheeyuan@163.com'\n\n# 袁天罡算命的结果（这里预留，每次由袁天罡生成后填入）\n# 格式要求：保持袁天罡原样，只在开头结尾加客套话\n\nZHAOCONG_INFO = \"\"\"\n- 性别：女\n- 出生：1998年1月11日（阳历），阴历1997年十二月初四\n- 出生地点：中国山东泰安\n- 居住地：德国波恩\n- 出生具体时间：暂不确定\n\"\"\"\n\ndef get_fortune_result():\n    \"\"\"这里会调用袁天罡来算命，结果填在这里\"\"\"\n    # TODO: 每次让袁天罡算完后更新这里\n    return \"\"\"（袁天罡算命结果）\"\"\"\n\ndef build_email_content(fortune_result):\n    \"\"\"构建邮件内容\"\"\"\n    today = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y年%m月%d日\")\n    \n    content = f\"\"\"{'='*50}\n\n赵丛，你好！\n\n{fortune_result}\n\n{'='*50}\n\n祝你今天顺利！\n\n袁天罡 敬上\n\n---\n*此邮件由翔宇代发\"\"\"\n    return content\n\ndef send_email(content):\n    \"\"\"发送邮件\"\"\"\n    msg = MIMEText(content, 'plain', 'utf-8')\n    msg['From'] = GMAIL\n    msg['To'] = TO_ZHAOCONG\n    msg['Cc'] = TO_LYNCH\n    msg['Subject'] = f'【袁天罡】赵丛 {today} 每日运势'\n    \n    server = smtplib.SMTP('smtp.gmail.com', 587)\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login(GMAIL, APP_PASSWORD)\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"邮件发送成功！\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # 获取今日运势\n    fortune = get_fortune_result()\n    \n    # 构建邮件\n    email_content = build_email_content(fortune)\n    \n    # 发送\n    send_email(email_content)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772778013666}}
{"type":"message","id":"39b12bdb","parentId":"7d028d47","timestamp":"2026-03-06T06:20:23.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到了这个脚本。现在我需要为赵丛计算今日运势。\n\n赵丛的信息：\n- 性别：女\n- 出生：1998年1月11日（阳历），阴历1997年十二月初四\n- 出生地点：中国山东泰安\n- 出生具体时间：暂不确定\n\n今日日期：2026年3月6日\n\n我需要计算八字。1998年1月11日的八字是什么？\n\n1998年1月11日：\n- 年柱：丁丑（1998年是戊寅年...不对，让我重新算）\n- 实际上1998年是虎年，天干是戊，地支是寅，所以是戊寅年\n- 但这是1998年1月11日，还在农历1997年十二月初四，所以年柱应该是1997年的丁丑\n\n让我仔细算一下：\n- 1998年1月11日对应阴历1997年十二月初四\n- 1997年是丁丑年（丁丑年）\n- 月柱：正月是寅月...但十二月初四还在腊月，应该是庚子月还是什么？\n- 日柱：需要查万年历\n- 时柱：未知\n\n我需要搜索一下赵丛的八字，或者用在线工具计算。让我搜索一下。\n\n另外，我需要了解今日的五行吉凶信息。让我先搜索一下2026年3月6日的五行八字信息。","thinkingSignature":"b0c66c9648c4b0d5e963b401fab2442af4a36f62258d2233d6f5238dbefcb278"},{"type":"text","text":"让我搜索一下赵丛的八字以及今日的运势信息。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vwrztzi5bxxb_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"1998年1月11日 阴历 1997年十二月初四 八字"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1040,"output":347,"cacheRead":15273,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16660,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772778013669}}
